          "description": "It seems odd to write a review of a parking garage, but here it is.\nI live in Connecticut and my daughter had to have heart surgery at NY Presbyterian.  After surgery, while they moved her to the ICU I needed to get my bag from the car (I valet at the entry).  They were so helpful that I needed to write this review.  I was an extremely distraught father and I am sure I looked horrible.  They could not have been kinder or more helpful.\nI have parked there every day since (running home and back) and they are always nice, and always helpful.",
